_sText:
Zm_rap_deadbase

This is my 2nd map. It has some similarities like my first map. It is pretty much balanced but still I made it a little easier for CTs. But it doesn't mean zombies can't win, they can with teamwork. It doesn't have a lot of places for building barricades but has a lot for climbing and camping. It's not very big but it is between big and medium but has a lot of places for camping.
